  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sri Arunodayam&apos;s &apos;Special Mom&apos; Award</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">There&apos;s no doubt about the mother&apos;s role in the life of her child - more  especially if it is a &apos;special&apos; child. In our society, however, mothers of &apos;special&apos; children are often misunderstood and judged. Some are even ostracized from their communities! But to us, these women are unsung heroes and we want to give them the honor they deserve. For not abandoning their children and displaying incredible courage, Sri Arunodayam is honoring 15 deserving &quot;Special Moms&quot;, in our 15th year of service.</narrative>
  </description>
